‚ćĚ SubForm Grid Demo - Tests Grid with embedded components inside SubForm
‚ćĚ Targets: Bug 6 (localStorage race), Grid event coordination, EdgeStyle on Grid

 EWC.SF_EVENT_COUNT‚Üź0

 'F1'eWC'Form' 'SubForm Grid Tests'(50 50)(590 700)('Coord' 'Pixel')

‚ćĚ --- SubForm containing Grid ---
‚ćĚ Posn (50,10) leaves clearance for the demo menu combo at top-right
 'F1.SF'eWC'SubForm'('Posn'(50 10))('Size'(490 660))('EdgeStyle' 'Ridge')

‚ćĚ Grid with Edit and Combo columns
 titles‚Üź'Name' 'Score' 'Grade'
 widths‚Üź120 80 80

 'F1.SF.G'eWC'Grid'('ColTitles' titles)('Posn'(10 10))('Size'(200 320))('TitleWidth' 40)('CellWidths' widths)('Event'('CellChanged' 'CellMove')'CBSubFormDemo')('ShowInput' 1)

‚ćĚ Input components for Grid columns
 'F1.SF.G.NAME'eWC'Edit'('Size'(23 120))
 'F1.SF.G.SCORE'eWC'Edit'('FieldType' 'Numeric')('Decimals' 0)('Size'(23 80))
 'F1.SF.G.GRADE'eWC'Combo'('Items'('A' 'B' 'C' 'D' 'F'))('Size'(23 80))

 inputs‚Üź'F1.SF.G.NAME' 'F1.SF.G.SCORE' 'F1.SF.G.GRADE'
 values‚Üź3 3‚ćī'Alice' '95' 'A' 'Bob' '82' 'B' 'Carol' '71' 'C'

 'F1.SF.G'eWS('Values' values)('CellTypes'(3 3‚ćī1 1 2))('Input' inputs)
 'F1.SF.G'eWS'CurCell'(1 1)

‚ćĚ Second simple Grid (Note: EdgeStyle is not supported on Grid components)
